'''文奴·雷·馬古斯'''（'''{{lang-pt|Manuel Rui Marques}}'''，{{bd|1977年|9月3日|catIdx=M}}）是一名[[安哥拉|安哥拉]]足球員，小時便移民至[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]，司職[[足球後衛|後衛]]。

==球員生涯==
===球會===
99/00球季，馬古斯加盟德國球會[[烏爾姆1846|烏爾姆1846]]，00/01球季便轉投[[哈化柏林足球會|哈化柏林]]，01/02球季轉投[[史特加足球會|史特加]]，並效力長達4季，04/05球季轉投[[馬里迪莫|馬里迪莫]]，及後利用[[博斯曼法案|博斯曼法案]]轉投列斯聯<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4708783.stm |title=Angolan Marques signs for Leeds |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2019-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902115453/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4708783.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

馬古斯為列斯聯首次上陣是[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]對[[奥特汉姆足球俱乐部|奧咸]]的賽事，但卻是當上他不熟悉的左閘<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/4168408.stm |title=Leeds 2-0 Oldham |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2019-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902031130/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/4168408.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，及後便外借至[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4837268.stm |title=Leeds complete Graham loan deal |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2020-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218005254/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/4837268.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，06/07球季，馬古斯重返列斯聯，但領隊[[丹尼斯·韋斯|丹尼斯·韋斯]]並不重用他，並讓他自由轉會，然而他卻努力地力求生存。

在2007年1月1日，馬古斯的毅力和堅持，令到他得以出戰[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]，在此戰，馬古斯充份表現出其中堅技術，令他重返一隊。然而，列斯聯卻降落[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]，但馬古斯卻未有離開球會，更於2007年8月7日與列斯聯簽下新合約<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/6935642.stm |title=Prutton and Marques pen new deals |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301141533/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/6935642.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

在2007年8月18日，馬古斯在列斯聯對[[修安联足球俱乐部|修安聯]]的賽事中，攻入加盟列斯聯以來的第一球，並助球隊大勝4-1<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6941782.stm |title=Leeds 4-1 Southend |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118042434/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6941782.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

在[[非洲國家盃|非洲國家盃]]期間，[[保羅·亨廷頓|保羅·亨廷頓]]一直代為出戰聯賽，其優秀表現取代了馬古斯的位置，令到該名[[安哥拉|安哥拉]]國腳只能作偶然替補上陣，由於馬古斯的合約將近結束，因此吸引了[[新特蘭足球會|新特蘭]]、[[屈福特足球會|屈福特]]和[[水晶宮足球俱樂部|水晶宮]]的注意<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rivals.net/news/pgarticle.aspx?artid=13662_3404574&id=42 |title=Championship Clubs On Their Marques |access-date=2008-05-23 |archive-date=2008-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080410230542/http://www.rivals.net/News/pgArticle.aspx?artid=13662_3404574&id=42 |dead-url=yes }}</ref></small>希望羅致馬古斯，但在現任列斯聯領隊[[加利·麥亞里士打|加利·麥亞里士打]]極力挽留下，最終在2008年5月20日與列斯聯簽定了兩年合約<small><ref>[http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/leedsunited/Rui39s-saved-me-a-job.4103772.jp Rui's saved me a job]{{Dead link|date=2020年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref></small>。

2010年5月14日，他被球會所放棄<ref>{{cite web |title=Leeds United trim squad after promotion |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8682477.stm |date=2010-05-04 |accessdate=2010-05-04 |publisher=BBC Sport |archive-date=2010-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100517054349/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8682477.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。


==國家隊==
[[安哥拉國家足球隊|安哥拉國家隊]]自1995年已致力尋找在國外而有[[安哥拉|安哥拉]]背景的球員加強實力，在7歲已移居[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]的馬古斯於2002年在[[德國|德國]][[斯图加特足球俱乐部|史特加]]時已被賞識<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/1951275.stm |title=Four in line for new Angola caps |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307042612/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/1951275.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但拒絕入伍<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/3004937.stm |title=Angolan shirt for Nando |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2012-09-09 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AYllS4xT?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/3004937.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。馬古斯在2005年年尾獲召加入國家隊備戰[[非洲國家盃|非洲國家盃]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4545026.stm |title=Angola call on defender Marques |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2019-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190830025124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4545026.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但其後落選決賽周大隊陣容<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/4601896.stm |title=Angola name new players for CAN |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211062738/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/4601896.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。安哥拉在非洲國家盃首輪分組賽出局後重整軍容備戰[[2006年世界盃足球賽|2006年世界盃]]，馬古斯獲選加入安哥拉<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/teams/angola/4770241.stm |title=Angola announce World Cup squad |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309111827/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/teams/angola/4770241.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2006年6月16日分組初賽第二場對[[墨西哥國家足球隊|墨西哥]]獲替補上場<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853058.stm |title=Mexico 0-0 Angola |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414130554/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853058.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，最後一場分組初賽對[[伊朗國家足球隊|伊朗]]同樣是替補上場<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853320.stm |title=Iran 1-1 Angola |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2017-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216230739/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853320.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，安哥拉3戰獲2分於分組初賽出局。

2007年12月20日，馬古斯獲選入翌年舉行的[[非洲國家盃|非洲國家盃]]的安哥拉初選名單<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/7153941.stm |title=Angola recall Marques for Ghana |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2019-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190904022021/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/7153941.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，並順利入選23人決選名單<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/7184850.stm |title=Angola stick with experience |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903222617/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/7184850.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2008年1月27日分組初賽首場後上3-1擊敗[[塞內加爾國家足球隊|塞內加爾]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/7210965.stm |title=Senegal 1-3 Angola |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211012103/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/7210965.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，次場0-0賽和[[突尼西亞國家足球隊|突尼西亞]]後已篤定晉級八強<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/7218825.stm |title=Tunisia 0-0 Angola |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2012-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406073320/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/7218825.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，2月4日八強戰1-2不敵最終冠軍[[埃及國家足球隊|埃及]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/7225288.stm |title=Egypt 2-1 Angola  |access-date=2008-04-09 |archive-date=2020-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104062634/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/7225288.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，結束馬古斯及「黑羚羊」（Palancas Negras）非洲國家盃之旅。

